Seeing:
{code}
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<GetBucketLocationResponse xmlns="http://s3.amazonaws.com/doc/2006-03-01/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"/>
{code}

should be:
{code}
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LocationConstraint xmlns="http://s3.amazonaws.com/doc/2006-03-01/"/>
{code}

This looks like more than just the empty location value, the response XML is wrong. We need to modify the response type completely.

[~shaon] I think I figured out a mapping that works, I can merge from dev/wwannemacher/EUCA-7708-3, or if you want, the important part is this - 

{code:xml}
	<mapping name="LocationConstraint" class="com.eucalyptus.objectstorage.msgs.GetBucketLocationResponseType">
		<value field="locationConstraint" style="text" usage="optional"/>
	</mapping>
{code}
